settings.custom_liquid:
{% comment %}
  Template: Careers
  This page highlights job openings, company culture, and career opportunities at Trezon.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="careers-container">
  <div class="careers-banner">
    <h1>Join the Trezon Team</h1>
    <p>Be part of a growing fashion brand that values creativity, innovation, and excellence.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="careers-content">
    <div class="careers-section">
      <h2>Why Work at Trezon?</h2>
      <p>At Trezon, we believe in creating a work environment that fosters growth, collaboration, and innovation. If you're passionate about fashion, sustainability, and making a difference, we'd love to have you on board!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="careers-section">
      <h2>Current Job Openings</h2>
      <p>We are always looking for talented individuals to join our team. Check out our latest opportunities below:</p>

      <div class="job-listings">
        <div class="job">
          <h3>Graphic Designer</h3>
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> Remote</p>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> Create visually stunning graphics for our products and marketing campaigns.</p>
          <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com?subject=Application%20for%20Graphic%20Designer" class="apply-button">Apply Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="job">
          <h3>Social Media Manager</h3>
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> Remote</p>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> Manage and grow our brand presence on social media platforms.</p>
          <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com?subject=Application%20for%20Social%20Media%20Manager" class="apply-button">Apply Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="job">
          <h3>Sales Executive</h3>
          <p><strong>Location:</strong> Delhi, India</p>
          <p><strong>Role:</strong> Drive sales and manage relationships with key clients.</p>
          <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com?subject=Application%20for%20Sales%20Executive" class="apply-button">Apply Now</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="careers-section">
      <h2>Internship Opportunities</h2>
      <p>Are you a student or recent graduate looking to gain hands-on experience? Join our internship program and work alongside industry experts.</p>
